**---Misc---**
[<@789298473735815187>` clear`] or [<@789298473735815187>` clear all`] or [<@789298473735815187>` clear number`]
	Attempts to delete the last `number` messages.
	If no number is specified, deletes a single message.
	If `all` is specified, deletes a large amount of messages.
	(ask bot owner for specific amount)
[<@789298473735815187>` owoify`]
	Owoifies or de-owoifies current channel.

**---Reaction Roles---**
[<@789298473735815187>` add reaction role role_id emoji`]
	Adds the role with id `role_id` to the reaction roles, associated with the emoji `emoji`.
[<@789298473735815187>` remove reaction role role_id`]
	Removes the role with id `role_id` from the reaction roles.
[<@789298473735815187>` reaction role message`]
	Creates a message to work with this server's reaction roles.
	The message is auto-updated. If you don't want it anymore, just delete it.
[<@789298473735815187>` list reaction roles`]
	List all reaction roles currently configured for this server.

2021-03-03 00:40:51.904000.author: rosarita
2021-03-03 00:40:51.904000.deleted_message:
**---Bans---**
[<@789298473735815187>` ban @user`] or [<@789298473735815187>` kill @user`]
	Bans mentioned user
[<@789298473735815187>` temp ban @user #h #m #s`] or [<@789298473735815187>` shoot @user #h #m #s`]
	Bans user for the duration specified,
	where `#` are numbers and `h`, `m` and `s`
	represent hours, minutes and seconds, respectively.
	(do note that once user has been unbanned, they still have to join the server themselves.
[<@789298473735815187>` unban user_id`]
	Unbans user with ID `user_id`
	**Do note that this command does not work with mentions, it needs the user's ID,
	since the user isn't, by definition, a part of the server.**

**---Mutes---**
**(these only work if mute roles were configured for this server)**
[<@789298473735815187>` mute @user`]
	Mutes mentioned user.
[<@789298473735815187>` temp mute @user #h #m #s`] or [<@789298473735815187>` arrest @user #h #m #s`]
	Mutes mentioned user for the duration specified,
	where `#` are numbers and `h`, `m` and `s`
	represent hours, minutes and seconds, respectively.
[<@789298473735815187>` unmute @user`]
	Unmutes mentioned user. (including both temporary and permanent mutes)

**---Warnings---**
[<@789298473735815187>` warn @user warning_message`]
	Warns mentioned user.
	Warning message will be either `warning_message` or a default message if none is given.
[<@789298473735815187>` remove warnings @user`] or [<@789298473735815187>` unwarn @user`]
	Removes all warnings for mentioned user.
[<@789298473735815187>` list warnings`] or [<@789298473735815187>` list warnings @user`]
	If a user is mentioned, list all of that user's warnings for this server.
	Otherwise, counts all warnings in this server, per user.
